{"tid":1563720,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友粗粗地整左個網出黎希望可以集合整理文宣","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T03:01:21.000Z","uid":257665,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7e09d5d0a5405d78013188e94f624a3cb279c89a","tid":1563720,"uid":257665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"主頁: <a href=\"https://www.mansuen.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mansuen.com&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=9c038c17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mansuen.com</a><br />\n<br />\n有時同朋友傾開計, 諗起係網上見過某張poster, 但一時三刻想搵出黎比對方睇係好難既, 所以就有個idea想集中一個地方收集文宣, 加入文字敘述, 方便記錄同搜尋.<br />\n<br />\n目前主要功能係每幅圖都有一堆tag, 一click就會filter晒有呢個tag既post. click user名都可以filter呢個user upload既文宣.<br />\n暫時只support圖片, 希望遲下可以support埋影片<br />\n<br />\n會努力持續更新"},{"pid":"6c33d0f60f627830add78968cec4d22fe30e866f","tid":1563720,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"cd9c4b358e22ab2cdbdf013c1a9f84d741e494c8","tid":1563720,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;